        <actionButtonLink>https://powerofus.force.com/s/article/NPSP-Merging-Contacts</actionButtonLink>
        <body>&lt;p&gt;Keeping your data clean and reliable is one of the most important ways to instill confidence in your system. Use NPSP Duplicate rules to identify duplicate contacts. Then use NPSP Contact Merge to merge duplicates into a single record without losing data from any related households, activities or opportunities. Learn best practices for managing duplicates.&lt;/p&gt;</body>
